ng a self-similarity in the hierarchy substructures\nwithin cluster mass halos.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2006 21:31:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Mar 2007 00:23:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
